snippet.textDisplay:
Esraj is so romantic. Charango sounds like madolin.
My mind explodes on just looking at the diversity of our native instruments. We must feel proud of our heritage and try to preserve it. 
Love the way Amit Trivedi has incorporated Rajasthani folk, no one else has done it in Coke Studio. 
Thanks for introducing us to first Mame Khan n now Kutle Khan. 
Kavita Seth's voice is so earthy. 
Sanjoy Das, Tapas Roy, Sanket are so talented.. 
Great composition by Amit & superbly played by all musicians... Loved it. Keep rocking ppl..

snippet.textDisplay:
I had heard about 400GB songs. Without music I can’t spend a breath.
When I put my stethoscope on a patient I found music there too.
I think after MR.A.R.Rahman,Mr.Amit Trivedi is the living legend,I always heard about music that a great musician should produce EAR SOOTHING SOUND,But,It’s not true.
Great music is what provide a great clean clearest visuals.
Thanks to Mr.Amit.
